  <front>
    <title>SCHC over PPP</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-thubert-lpwan-schc-over-ppp-00"/>
    <author initials="P." surname="Thubert" fullname="Pascal Thubert">
      <organization>Cisco Systems, Inc</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="03" month="December" year="2019"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document extends RFC 5172 to signal the use of SCHC as the
   compression method between a pair of nodes over PPP.  Combined with
   RFC 2516, this enables the use of SCHC over Ethernet and Wi-Fi.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
